OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRastafarian soldier wins   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fracism case against Army   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, One of the British Army's first        
OL,6, Rastafarian guardsmen has won a claim  
OL,7, of race discrimination and harassment  
OL,8, against the Ministry of Defence.       
OL,10,FDwight Pile-Gray says his 16-year Army 
OL,11,Fcareer was brought to an end following 
OL,12,Fa row at a guardroom, in which a white 
OL,13,Fguard didn't believe he was a soldier. 
OL,15,FWhen he challenged the soldier, he was 
OL,16,Faccused of "playing the race card". He 
OL,17,Fwon his case at an employment tribunal.
OL,19,FThe MoD said it did not tolerate abuse,
OL,20,Fbullying or discrimination of any kind.
